{
  "stem": "10829.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had enough food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And food was richness in those days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a lot different than richness now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you could study, you could sit, you learn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We considered a rich man if you knew the Gemara, and you knew the-- you could sit down on Shabbos and talk and [YIDDISH] Gemara.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But a rabbi, you were a rich man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You went to yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Like my uncle, he was a rich man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we-- our house by itself to describe was-- we didn't have any floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We used to put on hay on there, and every Friday night used to go to with a rake and clean it up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had-- that was the type of house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And back of the house, we had our barn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a hothouse and everything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And back as far as you could see was our land, and we used to farm it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We'd raise almost everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the life was real simple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it was real relaxed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I mean, you-- you had people that would come into the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You didn't have any locks and keys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The only thing basic we had to worry is about the goyim to come in and eat or kill you or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But as far as the city life, was real simple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "In our city, the-- the exception was when somebody was not keeping the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "A goy was considered the outcast of the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "God forbid you don't go to schul on Shabbos, you were the outcast of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You know, this guy is-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You know, he's-- this was an outcast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "In Europe, in Europe, religion was looked-- at least what I know of, what I have experienced-- was looked a lot different than here.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
